Detailed Description

Parameters:
QCI 
  • QOS specified using the QOS Class Identifier (QOS) values QCI value 0 - Requests the network to assign the appropriate QCI value QCI values 1-4 - Associated with guaranteed bit rates QCI values 5-9 - Associated with non-guaranteed bit rates
gDlBitRate 
  • Guaranteed DL bit rate

gUlBitRate

maxUlBitRate
